#

Roasted Lemon Herb Chicken with Garlic Mashed Potatoes

$15.99
750 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

DairyGarlic

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

Main CourseComfort FoodFamily Friendly

Description

Juicy roasted chicken infused with bright lemon and aromatic herbs, served with creamy garlic mashed potatoes.

Ingredients

  • Whole Chicken: 1 (3-4 lbs)
  • Lemon: 2, juiced and zested
  • Fresh Rosemary: 2 sprigs
  • Fresh Thyme: 2 sprigs
  • Olive Oil: 1/4 cup
  • Garlic: 6 cloves, minced
  • Salt: 1 tablespoon
  • Black Pepper: 1 teaspoon
  • Potatoes: 2 lbs, peeled and cubed
  • Butter: 4 tablespoons
  • Heavy Cream: 1/2 cup
